data.description: When approaching this home, you immediately think about the potential it can have, the grand design and uniqueness of what older homes can provide. Entering the home gives you the impression that it is bigger than you would think from outside and great layout for those who love this area home. Having 4 bedrooms, 1.1 bathrooms and a basement allows for plenty of space for living and storage. Come take a look at this one as it is conveniently located near downtown Elgin, Lords Park, I-90 and much more.
